  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为任务状态流转设计一个状态图。核心流程是从待办开始，经过开发中、测试、评审，最后完成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ToDo",
        "InProgress",
        "Test",
        "InReview",
        "Done"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，起点是[*]到ToDo。我想确认一下，Blocked状态是否也需要纳入？比如任务遇到障碍的情况。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "ToDo",
        "Blocked"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Blocked很重要。任务在开始前、开发中、测试阶段、评审阶段都可能被阻塞。每个场景回到的后续状态不一样。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Blocked",
        "ToDo",
        "InProgress",
        "Test",
        "InReview"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那我先画主干：ToDo通过\"Rozpoczęcie pracy\"到InProgress，然后\"Gotowe do testów\"到Test，再\"Testy pomyślne\"到InReview，最后\"Zaakceptowane\"到Done。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ToDo",
        "InProgress",
        "Test",
        "InReview",
        "Done"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "主干没问题。但Test失败的情况呢？需要能回到InProgress修复。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Test",
        "InProgress"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Test到InProgress的转换，标注为\"Testy wykazały błędy\"。现在处理Blocked的流入：ToDo可以通过\"Zidentyfikowano przeszkodę (przed rozpoczęciem)\"进入Blocked。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Test",
        "InProgress",
        "ToDo",
        "Blocked"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Blocked的流出要细分。如果阻塞前没进过InProgress，解除后回ToDo；如果已经在InProgress过，或者可以直接开始，就回到InProgress。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Blocked",
        "ToDo",
        "InProgress"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "理解，标注分别是\"Usunięto przeszkodę (nie było w InProgress)\"和\"Usunięto przeszkodę (było w InProgress lub można rozpocząć)\"。那如果阻塞前在Test或InReview呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Blocked",
        "Test",
        "InReview"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "同样要回去，标注\"było w Test\"和\"było w InReview\"。另外InProgress本身也可能被阻塞，标注\"w trakcie realizacji\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Blocked",
        "Test",
        "InReview",
        "InProgress"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加这四条Blocked流出和InProgress到Blocked的流入。Test和InReview到Blocked的转换我也加上，分别标注\"w trakcie testów\"和\"w trakcie przeglądu\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Blocked",
        "Test",
        "InReview",
        "InProgress"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "InReview还有两条流出：需要开发修改时回InProgress，标注\"Konieczne zmiany deweloperskie\"；接受后去Done。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "InReview",
        "InProgress",
        "Done"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已完成。还有Done到[*]的终态。我注意到InProgress到ToDo有一条回流，是什么场景？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Done",
        "[*]",
        "InProgress",
        "ToDo"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "那是\"Cofnięcie do puli\"，比较少见的情况，标注\"rzadziej\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "InProgress",
        "ToDo"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，已添加。让我核对一下所有状态：[*]→ToDo→InProgress→Test→InReview→Done→[*]，加上Blocked的六条流入和四条流出，以及各阶段的回流。结构完整吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "ToDo",
        "InProgress",
        "Test",
        "InReview",
        "Done",
        "Blocked"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "稍等，InReview到Done的标注我确认一下——应该是\"Zaakceptowane\"，不是\"zaakcept\"，要完整拼写。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "InReview",
        "Done"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "已修正为\"Zaakceptowane\"。另外\"Rozpoczęcie pracy\"我简写为\"Rozp\"可以吗？还是保持完整？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ToDo",
        "InProgress"
      ],
